from.name: R I A N N A  Skywalker

data.name:
Yesterday we went into the 4th day of this LOVE story... birthday LOVE to all my fellow Mayan Family members who are now taking on the mantel of being

RED - initiating, igniting, firing up
SELF EXISTING - the form, structure, the definition and measurement
SKYWALKER - cosmic connector, bridge between heaven and earth...

Ah this love story is so precious... we dive into LOVE, polarised and then worked through what came up, somehow integrating the opposing forces, channelling all that emotional energy into healing, and doing what best releases and expresses those diverse and complex feelings... we made a space to connect to Spirit with our beingness... and now... we enter the form of love... THE SHAPE THAT LOVE IS...

This day, and your year, the story of LOVE is about bringing Heaven to EARTH.... Skywalker... we are now ready to go beyond, beyond our wounds, beyond the oppositions and the process of emotions... to travel into the STARS and beyond... elevating ourselves to our Divine Natures... and exploring the Space that LOVE creates... LOVE is the softest most accepting space, the space of utter surrender and trust, the space of unconditional being, unconditional love... LOVE is SPACE... but not an empty space, a space filled with connectivity... Skywalker is the connection... In HUMAN we are dealing with what is inside, our emotions and feelings... next step up the evolutionary journey, we step out of our small self, and connect to our cosmic self which is connected beyond to the UNIVERSAL SOURCE OF ALL THAT IS...

We all have had these moments of feeling how loves opens us up, the huge space of the heart and how cosmic it all feels... this is the house of LOVE that we must build... the temple of LOVE in which we reside... the temple we create inside, but also around us, and our relationships, and community... Self Existing Skywalker reminds us that we must keep space in our LOVE story... the space to grow... not a disconnected space, a space of trust, and divine guidance.... 

As Kahil Gibran in The Prophet says :

“Let there be spaces in your togetherness, And let the winds of the heavens dance between you. 

Love one another but make not a bond of love: Let it rather be a moving sea between the shores of your souls. 

Fill each other's cup but drink not from one cup. Give one another of your bread but eat not from the same loaf. 

Sing and dance together and be joyous, but let each one of you be alone, Even as the strings of a lute are alone though they quiver with the same music. 

Give your hearts, but not into each other's keeping. For only the hand of Life can contain your hearts. 

And stand together, yet not too near together: For the pillars of the temple stand apart, And the oak tree and the cypress grow not in each other's shadow.”

Guiding this day, your year, is MOON, the hidden power we attained the day before, this is the sensitivity and flow of the universal waters, the feminine... softness and surrender, to be a Skywalker bridging heaven to earth, there can be no agenda, no control, there is only allowing spirit to move you towards the connection that is to be made... the journey is not directed from the mind or ego, it's pure surrender of the HEART... and to the feminine... the HOUSE OF LOVE is one in which the feminine is EXALTED... in men and in women... The form of LOVE and relating must be subject to the cycles of life, the ebbing and flowing of the moon - the intensity of emotions will ebb and flow... we must allow this, and as we do, this will purify our space of LOVE... and more love will flow... 

Supporting this day, and your year, is Worldbridger - death, change and renewal, as we go beyond, we must let go, and allow what needs to die, to die, and what needs to change to change, so that the energy can flow and be renewed.... Worldbridger like Skywalker is connecting beyond the small self... to the wider cosmos, and different realms as well as within this realm, extending... relating is always asking us to go beyond, to die to ourself perception, so that we can grow into much more than we imagined.... This is a major key in our LOVE stories... often through fear and control, we try to keep everything the same, keep ourselves the same and our partners the same, and then we are no more in the space of LOVE... we have killed it, as we have deadened ourselves... Worldbridger here reminds us that we must allow the changes that bring us to the best of ourselves... and to trust that LOVE is leading us that way... LOVE LIGHTS THE WAY...

Challenging this day, and your year, is NIGHT... so now we are in LOVE, and we enter the void, of not knowing... we must, because if we know, we have defined and therefore we have be-littled all possibilities... so the challenge as we attempt to go beyond, is the let go, allowing the change, being happy to ride through the darkness, and trusting only our dreams and intuition that lie there, no more mentalising, we cannot fathom with our minds the complexity of UNIVERSAL LOVE... but in our dreams and intuition we are given glimpses... and so between these two states we are integrating when to surrender, and what to change.... 

The hidden power emerging from this process will be STAR, beauty, elegance and the arts... the house of LOVE is beautiful... as we create the space for LOVE to flourish, we beautify ourselves and the space around us... COSMIC love is the heavenly beauty of the universe.... in the story of LOVE, creating the temple of LOVE will allow the beauty of LOVE to shine stronger and longer for all... 

What a beautiful journey, enjoy and embrace the space of LOVE for yourself, and in doing so, allow others also to share that space with you, or be moved to create that space for themselves...

VIVE LA LOVULUTION
